TOGETHER,

14:04.437 --> 14:09.676
BUT IT DOESN'T WORK,
NONE OF IT.

14:09.676 --> 14:15.381
UNLESS YOU'VE LOST A CHILD,
YOU DON'T GET IT.

14:15.381 --> 14:17.818
