14:44.745 --> 14:47.480
I WAS SO ANGRY.

14:47.480 --> 14:50.584
♪♪♪♪

14:50.584 --> 14:53.486
PEOPLE SAY
THE DUMBEST THINGS.

14:53.486 --> 14:58.525
AND THEY MEAN WELL.
THEY REALLY DO.

14:58.525 --> 15:00.801
BUT NOTHING
WOULD COMFORT ME.

15:00.801 --> 15:05.672
♪♪♪♪

15:05.672 --> 15:11.778
BUT A REALLY GOOD FRIEND
GAVE ME SOME GREAT ADVICE.

15:14.515 --> 15:16.917
SHE SAYS
IT COMES IN WAVES.

15:21.054 --> 15:24.758
YOU NEED TO PRAY.

15:24.758 --> 15:26.693
GOD SENT YOU THIS GRIEF
IN WAVES

15:26.693 --> 15:30.196
SO IT DOESN'T
OVERWHELM YOU.

15:30.196 --> 15:34.901
♪♪♪♪

15:34.901 --> 15:38.438
OH, I HOPE HE SENDS IT
TO YOU IN WAVES.

15:43.777 --> 15:46.647
I DON'T FEEL NOTHING.

15:46.647 --> 15:50.951
♪♪♪♪

15:50.951 --> 15:53.219
NOTHING AT ALL.

15:53.219 --> 15:57.824
IT'S ‐‐

15:57.824 --> 16:00.734
