TO FEEL NOTHING.

16:00.734 --> 16:03.303
♪♪♪♪

16:03.303 --> 16:06.439
I KNOW THAT FEELING.

16:06.439 --> 16:07.774
IT PASSES.

16:11.044 --> 16:16.917
AND THERE'S SUCH SADNESS
AND DEPRESSION

16:16.917 --> 16:18.418
AND RAGE AND ANGER,

16:18.418 --> 16:20.621
AND IT'S A BITCH.

16:20.621 --> 16:23.657
♪♪♪♪

16:23.657 --> 16:26.827
AND THEN THERE'S
JUST YOU

16:26.827 --> 16:35.536
SETTLING TO
A...NEW WAY OF LIVING,

16:35.536 --> 16:37.538
A NEW WAY OF NORMAL.

16:37.538 --> 16:40.574
♪♪♪♪

16:43.810 --> 16:47.013
A NEW WAY OF NORMAL?

16:47.013 --> 16:49.149
YES.

16:49.149 --> 16:52.519
♪♪♪♪

16:52.519 --> 16:58.892
THERE'S NOTHING NORMAL
ABOUT THIS MUCH STRUGGLE

16:58.892 --> 17:01.968
AND THIS MUCH PAIN.

17:01.968 --> 17:05.005
♪♪♪♪

17:09.375 --> 17:13.146
MY LIFE HAS BEEN
FROM NOTHING TO NOTHING.

17:13.146 --> 17:18.519
NOW DON'T SAY THAT.
IT'S THE TRUTH.

17:18.519 --> 17:23.389
I HAVE HAD SUCH
STRONG FAITH, BUT...

17:25.959 --> 17:29.630
THIS RIGHT HERE,

17:29.630 --> 17:34.701
THIS ‐‐
THIS RIGHT HERE,

17:34.701 --> 17:38.338
GOD, YOU GOT
SOME EXPLAINING TO DO.

17:38.338 --> 17:41.842
HANNA. SHH.

17:41.842 --> 17:47.614
I'VE DONE MY BEST
TO LIVE MY LIFE RIGHT NOW,

17:47.614 --> 17:52.152
BUT I GET UPSET.

17:52.152 --> 17:57.157
I GET MAD.
NO, I GET PISSED OFF.

17:57.157 --> 18:02.670
