MY BEST TO DO MY BEST.

18:03.637 --> 18:05.972
AND WHAT GOOD IS IT?

18:05.972 --> 18:07.407
HUH?

18:07.407 --> 18:16.285
I MEAN, THAT BABY IS IN THERE
ON A C‐COLD, STEEL TABLE.

18:16.617 --> 18:19.553
♪♪♪♪

18:19.553 --> 18:23.156
WHAT GOOD IS THAT?

18:23.156 --> 18:26.126
OH, GOD.

18:26.126 --> 18:27.828
OH, GOD.

18:27.828 --> 18:28.895
HANNA.
TALK TO ME.

18:28.895 --> 18:30.897
HANNA.

18:30.897 --> 18:34.267
HANNA.

18:34.267 --> 18:36.336
MOM.

18:36.336 --> 18:39.372
WHAT?!

18:39.372 --> 18:40.641
YOU'RE OKAY.

18:40.641 --> 18:42.843
I KNOW!
I KNOW I'M OKAY!

18:42.843 --> 18:44.778
I KNOW I'M FINE!

18:44.778 --> 18:47.748
BUT HE IS NOT.
HE IS DEAD!

18:47.748 --> 18:49.550
MOM.
DO YOU UNDERSTAND THAT?

18:49.550 --> 18:52.152
DO YOU
UNDERSTAND THAT?

18:52.152 --> 18:54.054
HE IS DEAD!

18:54.054 --> 18:55.622
HE IS DEAD!

18:55.622 --> 18:57.357
HE IS DEAD!

18:57.357 --> 19:01.535
HE IS DEAD!

19:01.535 --> 19:03.637
HE IS DEAD!

19:03.637 --> 19:04.705
PLEASE, MAMA, RELAX.

19:04.705 --> 19:07.140
[ CRYING ]

19:07.140 --> 19:10.176
♪♪♪♪

19:16.349 --> 19:19.786
LET HER GO, BENNY.
LET HER GO.

19:19.786 --> 19:22.155
LET HER GO, BENNY.

19:22.155 --> 19:25.191
♪♪♪♪

19:34.134 --> 19:36.603
COME ON.

19:36.603 --> 19:39.740
COME ON. COME ON.

19:39.740 --> 19:43.577
♪♪♪♪

19:43.577 --> 19:46.112
COME ON.

19:46.112 --> 19:48.582
LET'S COME BACK
TO MY HOUSE.

19:48.582 --> 19:51.317
I'LL TAKE YOU HOME.

19:51.317 --> 19:55.589
♪♪♪♪

19:55.589 --> 19:59.359
I'LL TAKE YOU HOME.

20:05.338 --> 20:08.374
♪♪♪♪

20:12.546 --> 20:13.914
YOU KNOW WHAT?

20:13.914 --> 20:16.016
SO, YOU'RE WANTED?
GET OUT.

20:16.016 --> 20:17.651
I CAN'T HELP YOU OUT
WITH THIS WARRANT.

20:17.651 --> 20:19.319
I DIDN'T ASK YOU TO.

20:19.319 --> 20:22.188
YOU TOOK ALL MY SURVEILLANCE
OUT OF THE ROOM.

20:22.188 --> 20:26.927
YEAH, AND I'LL DO IT AGAIN
WHEN YOU LEAVE.

20:26.927 --> 20:28.228
YOU DO KNOW I'M PAYING
FOR THIS ROOM, RIGHT?

20:28.228 --> 20:30.496
DOES IT LOOK
LIKE I CARE?

20:30.496 --> 20:33.800
OH, I THINK YOU DO.

20:33.800 --> 20:35.101
YOU GOT NOWHERE TO GO.

20:35.101 --> 20:37.370
YOU CAN'T GO HOME.

20:37.370 --> 20:39.439
YOU MIGHT WANT TO BE
A LITTLE NICER TO ME.

20:39.439 --> 20:42.709
I DON'T HAVE TO DO
ANYTHING FOR YOU. NOW LEAVE.

20:42.709 --> 20:44.911
CANDACE, LOOK.
THIS IS IMPORTANT.

20:44.911 --> 20:46.346
WHAT'S IMPORTANT?

20:46.346 --> 20:48.414
I NEED YOU TO ‐‐

20:48.414 --> 20:51.484
WHAT? WHAT DO YOU WANT
FROM HIM AND WHY?

20:51.484 --> 20:52.986
I JUST NEED ‐‐

20:52.986 --> 20:55.255
JUST WHAT YOU DID
LAST NIGHT, OKAY?

20:55.255 --> 20:56.757
I'M BEING PAID
BY SOME POWERFUL PEOPLE

20:56.757 --> 20:58.458
WHO WANT HIM
OUT OF THE RACE.

20:58.458 --> 21:00.801
[ SCOFFS ]
IT'S TOO LATE.

21:00.801 --> 21:02.468
HE'S GOING TO WIN.

21:02.468 --> 21:03.436
NO. NO, HE'S NOT.

21:03.436 --> 21:05.606
NOT IF YOU DO
WHAT I NEED DONE, OKAY?

21:05.606 --> 21:07.841
LOOK, THIS GUY, HE ‐‐
HE ACTS LIKE HE'S A CHOIRBOY,

21:07.841 --> 21:11.612
BUT HE'S NOT.
NOBODY'S THAT CLEAN.

21:11.612 --> 21:13.880
NOW, LOOK ‐‐ I GOT
HIRED MONTHS AGO TO GET HIM,

21:13.880 --> 21:16.449
BUT I HAVEN'T BEEN ABLE
TO GET ANY DIRT ON HIM.

21:16.449 --> 21:19.520
YOU WERE THE FIRST PERSON
THAT'S GOTTEN IN SOMEWHAT,

21:19.520 --> 21:21.187
AND WHAT YOU HAVE
IS GOLD.

21:21.187 --> 21:24.725
I NEED TO STOP
HIS MOMENTUM.

21:24.725 --> 21:26.960
AND WHY
WOULD I HELP YOU?

21:26.960 --> 21:28.394
BECAUSE
I WOULD BE HELPING YOU.

21:28.394 --> 21:30.797
AND HOW IS THAT?

21:30.797 --> 21:32.866
BECAUSE YOU WOULD BE
FIRST LADY OF THE UNITED STATES.

21:32.866 --> 21:34.868
OH, PLEASE.

21:34.868 --> 21:36.703
YOU COULD BE.

21:36.703 --> 21:38.605
THERE'S SOMETHING
CALLED VETTING,

21:38.605 --> 21:40.541
AND I WOULDN'T PASS IT.
YEAH, WELL, WITH MY HELP ‐‐

21:40.541 --> 21:44.010
MY FACE IS ALL OVER THE TV,
WANTED FOR MURDER.

21:44.010 --> 21:45.579
ALL THAT CAN BE SPUN.
GET OUT.

21:45.579 --> 21:47.113
LOOK,
I'M TELLING YOU ‐‐

21:47.113 --> 21:51.451
NO, THIS DOESN'T ‐‐
THIS DOESN'T MAKE ANY SENSE.

21:51.451 --> 21:54.154
EVEN IF I GIVE YOU DIRT,
HOW WOULD I BECOME

21:54.154 --> 21:57.691
THE FIRST LADY,
AS SILLY AS IT SOUNDS?

21:57.691 --> 22:00.026
NOT NOW, BUT IN EIGHT YEARS.
IN EIGHT YEARS?

22:00.026 --> 22:02.736
CANDACE, KEEP YOUR VOICE DOWN!
HE'S RIGHT NEXT DOOR!

22:02.736 --> 22:04.638
NOT NOW, BUT IN EIGHT YEARS,
ALL RIGHT?

22:04.638 --> 22:06.439
MY GUY WINS THIS TIME,
AND IN EIGHT YEARS,

22:06.439 --> 22:07.908
YOU PROP HIM UP,
AND YOU HELP HIM HEAL.

22:07.908 --> 22:11.144
ALL RIGHT?
YOU LET HIM WIN.

22:11.144 --> 22:12.478
EIGHT YEARS.

22:12.478 --> 22:15.248
CANDACE,
THIS IS THE LONG GAME.

22:15.248 --> 22:17.350
I'M NOT IN IT
FOR THE LONG GAME.

22:17.350 --> 22:19.452
WELL,
THAT'S YOUR PROBLEM.

22:19.452 --> 22:20.587
YOU LOOK
FOR THE QUICK BUCK,

22:20.587 --> 22:22.422
AND THAT'S WHY
YOU DON'T HAVE ONE NOW.

22:22.422 --> 22:23.456
YOU SPEND
YOUR WHOLE LIFE

22:23.456 --> 22:24.558
TRIPPING OVER POWER
TO GET MONEY.

22:24.558 --> 22:26.226
AND THERE'S
A DIFFERENCE, CANDACE.

22:26.226 --> 22:28.562
POWER BEGETS MONEY.
MONEY DON'T BEGET POWER.

22:28.562 --> 22:30.330
GET OUT.

22:30.330 --> 22:32.232
AGAIN, I'M PAYING
FOR THIS ROOM.

22:32.232 --> 22:33.734
I CAN LEAVE RIGHT NOW.

22:33.734 --> 22:35.001
WHAT, AND GO WHERE?

22:35.001 --> 22:36.537
WHEREVER THE HELL
I WANT TO GO.

22:36.537 --> 22:38.572
I WAS MAKING IT BEFORE YOU,
AND I'LL MAKE IT AFTER YOU.

22:38.572 --> 22:40.140
NO, YOU WERE HUSTLING
LOW‐LIVES BEFORE ME.

22:40.140 --> 22:43.009
THIS RIGHT HERE,
THIS IS THE BIG LEAGUES.

22:43.009 --> 22:45.011
OH, SO, YOU WANT
TO BE MY PIMP?

22:45.011 --> 22:48.114
NO, I WANT TO BE
YOUR PARTNER.

22:48.114 --> 22:49.783
LEAVE.

22:49.783 --> 22:51.317
JUST GIVE ME
WHAT YOU HAVE ON HIM,

22:51.317 --> 22:54.054
AND I'LL TAKE IT FROM THERE.
HE'LL NEVER KNOW WHAT HAPPENED.

22:54.054 --> 22:55.321
I DON'T HAVE ANYTHING.

22:55.321 --> 22:58.224
I KNOW YOU, CANDACE.
YES, YOU DO.

22:58.224 --> 23:00.767
I DON'T.

23:00.767 --> 23:02.268
CANDACE.

23:02.268 --> 23:05.672
GET OUT.

23:05.672 --> 23:07.340
HE'S GOING TO BE HERE
FOR THREE MORE DAYS,

23:07.340 --> 23:10.677
AND AFTER THAT,
HE'S GOING BACK TO D. C.

23:10.677 --> 23:12.345
GET HIM.

23:12.345 --> 23:15.381
♪♪♪♪

23:35.902 --> 23:38.939
♪♪♪♪

23:41.875 --> 23:43.844
MRS. HARRINGTON?
YES?

23:43.844 --> 23:46.713
I'M DR. VINCENTE.
HI. HOW'S THE BABY?

23:46.713 --> 23:48.915
WELL, THE MOTHER'S FINE.
HOW IS THE BABY?

23:48.915 --> 23:52.218
THE BABY'S FINE.
OH, GOOD.

23:52.218 --> 23:55.488
UH, BUT SHE LOST
A LOT OF BLOOD, AND WE'RE ‐‐

23:55.488 --> 23:57.558
DOES THAT
AFFECT THE BABY?

23:57.558 --> 24:00.360
WELL, WE'RE GIVING HER
BLOOD NOW, BUT IT LOOKS LIKE ‐‐

24:00.360 --> 24:04.170
THE BABY.
THE BABY. THE BABY.

24:04.170 --> 24:06.873
SHE AND THE BABY
WILL BE FINE.

24:06.873 --> 24:09.309
THAT'S GREAT.
WOULD YOU LIKE TO SEE HER?

24:09.309 --> 24:11.578
NO, I HAVE
SOME THINGS TO DO,

24:11.578 --> 24:12.946
SO PLEASE LET ME KNOW

24:12.946 --> 24:15.148
IF ANYTHING CHANGES
WITH THE BABY.

24:15.148 --> 24:17.584
MRS. HARRINGTON, WE NEED TO TALK
ABOUT COUNSELING FOR HER.

24:17.584 --> 24:20.787
SHE'S VERY DEPRESSED.

24:20.787 --> 24:24.490
IS THIS DEPRESSION
AFFECTING THE BABY?

24:24.490 --> 24:27.127
UH, IT'S ‐‐
SERIOUSLY.

24:27.127 --> 24:29.295
I'M NOT SURE.

24:29.295 --> 24:30.864
BUT, IF SHE
HARMS HERSELF ‐‐

24:30.864 --> 24:32.999
OH, SHE WON'T
DO THAT AGAIN.

24:32.999 --> 24:34.601
HOW CAN YOU BE SO SURE?

24:34.601 --> 24:37.003
WHEN I'M DONE TALKING TO HER,
SHE WILL NEVER DO THAT AGAIN.

24:37.003 --> 24:38.471
TRUST ME.

24:38.471 --> 24:41.575
OKAY. WOULD YOU
LIKE TO SEE HER?

24:41.575 --> 24:43.744
NO.

24:43.744 --> 24:46.713
YOU KNOW, SEEING A FRIENDLY FACE
MIGHT BE GOOD FOR HER.

24:46.713 --> 24:51.552
WHICH IS EXACTLY WHY
I DON'T WANT TO SEE HER.

24:51.552 --> 24:53.386
OKAY.

24:53.386 --> 24:55.989
THANK YOU SO MUCH,
DOCTOR.

24:55.989 --> 24:57.991
THAT'S GREAT.

24:57.991 --> 24:59.693
COME ON, JEFFERY.
LET'S GO HOME.

24:59.693 --> 25:03.804
I WANT TO SEE HER.
WHAT?

25:03.804 --> 25:06.306
YEAH.

25:06.306 --> 25:08.441
WHY?

25:08.441 --> 25:10.276
BECAUSE
I WANT TO CHECK ON HER.

25:13.446 --> 25:14.815
NO, YOU DON'T.

25:14.815 --> 25:17.150
WHAT?

25:17.150 --> 25:19.452
YOU WANT TO GO SEE WYATT,
DON'T YOU?

25:19.452 --> 25:22.022
♪♪♪♪

25:22.022 --> 25:26.359
YES, HIM, TOO.

25:26.359 --> 25:28.228
NOT TONIGHT.

25:28.228 --> 25:29.863
COME ON, JEFFERY.
LET'S GO HOME.

25:29.863 --> 25:31.431
COME ON.

25:31.431 --> 25:33.934
♪♪♪♪

25:33.934 --> 25:35.869
DAMN IT, BOY.

25:35.869 --> 25:38.905
♪♪♪♪

25:49.650 --> 25:52.352
JIM.

25:52.352 --> 25:54.220
YEAH.

25:54.220 --> 25:56.489
[ CLEARS THROAT ]
HI.

25:56.489 --> 25:59.993
HI.

25:59.993 --> 26:02.035
SO, WHAT'S
GOING ON, ROSE?

26:02.035 --> 26:05.071
I'M NOT
A HAPPY WOMAN.

26:05.071 --> 26:07.207
I CAN SEE THAT.

26:07.207 --> 26:10.276
AND YOU KNOW WHAT I'M LIKE
WHEN I'M NOT HAPPY.

26:10.276 --> 26:14.280
YES, I DO.
IT'S NOT GOOD.

26:14.280 --> 26:16.449
NO, IT'S NOT.

26:16.449 --> 26:19.753
DO YOU REMEMBER
WHAT HAPPENED IN '08?

26:19.753 --> 26:21.387
YES.

26:21.387 --> 26:23.624
DO YOU REMEMBER
THE RACE RIOTS?

26:23.624 --> 26:24.891
VIVIDLY.

26:24.891 --> 26:26.827
WELL, I'M THAT ANGRY.

26:26.827 --> 26:30.296
♪♪♪♪

26:30.296 --> 26:33.099
OKAY, SO WHAT CAN I DO
FOR YOU, ROSE?

26:33.099 --> 26:38.238
YOU CAN TELL ME WHO THE HELL
THIS WAR KID IS.

26:38.238 --> 26:42.408
WAR IS SOME THUG
OFF THE STREETS.

26:42.408 --> 26:46.647
HOW DO YOU KNOW HIM?

26:46.647 --> 26:49.750
DO YOU REMEMBER CANDACE?

26:49.750 --> 26:51.852
THAT GIRL THAT YOU
WOULDN'T LET ME TAKE OUT.

26:51.852 --> 26:54.755
YEAH, HER.

26:54.755 --> 26:58.191
GO ON.

26:58.191 --> 27:01.034
SHE HAD WAR ABDUCT ME.

27:01.034 --> 27:03.604
THIS KID?
YEAH.

27:03.604 --> 27:06.807
A FEDERAL JUDGE?
YEAH.

27:06.807 --> 27:11.277
IS HE AN IDIOT?
[ CHUCKLES ] YEAH. YES.

27:11.277 --> 27:14.314
SO, HE ABDUCTS YOU.

27:14.314 --> 27:17.283
AND HE HAD ME HELD
FOR RANSOM.

27:17.283 --> 27:19.052
HOW MUCH RANSOM?

27:19.052 --> 27:21.487
$7.4 MILLION.

27:21.487 --> 27:23.924
HE'S AN IDIOT.

27:23.924 --> 27:27.628
YES, BUT HE'S AN IDIOT WHO WAS
JUST BEING A PUPPET FOR CANDACE.

27:27.628 --> 27:29.229
GO ON.

27:29.229 --> 27:33.266
♪♪♪♪

27:33.266 --> 27:36.036
OKAY, SO, HE FINDS OUT

27:36.036 --> 27:38.772
THAT SHE CHEATED HIM
OUT OF A BUNCH OF MONEY.

27:38.772 --> 27:41.742
SHE HAD HIM SET UP.
SHE PUT DRUGS IN HIS CAR,

27:41.742 --> 27:43.877
AND HE WAS PISSED.

27:43.877 --> 27:47.748
SO, I MET HIM IN JAIL,
AND WE STRUCK UP A DEAL.

27:47.748 --> 27:50.316
WHAT WAS THE DEAL?

27:50.316 --> 27:52.218
CANDACE HAD
SOMETHING I NEEDED.

27:54.254 --> 27:58.992
I'M NOT IN THE MOOD
TO PULL THINGS OUT OF YOU.

27:58.992 --> 28:03.369
PICTURES OF ME IN
COMPROMISING POSITIONS, OKAY?

28:03.369 --> 28:07.941
WAR'S JOB WAS TO GO GET
THE PICTURES BACK FOR ME.

28:07.941 --> 28:11.712
SO, THAT'S WHY YOU HAD
DAVID GET HIM OUT.

28:11.712 --> 28:13.313
YES.

28:13.313 --> 28:15.148
MM‐KAY.

28:15.148 --> 28:17.718
SO, MY SOURCES
WERE RIGHT.

28:17.718 --> 28:20.186
♪♪♪♪

28:20.186 --> 28:21.955
YES.

28:21.955 --> 28:26.793
YOU KNOW, I HAVE ALWAYS
BEEN THERE FOR YOU.

28:26.793 --> 28:29.630
♪♪♪♪

28:29.630 --> 28:31.932
AS I HAVE ALWAYS
BEEN THERE FOR YOU.

28:31.932 --> 28:35.669
YES, I KNOW.

28:35.669 --> 28:39.039
SO, WHAT THE HELL IS THIS ABOUT,
ROSE? WHAT HAPPENED?

28:39.039 --> 28:42.042
THAT SON OF A BITCH
WENT AFTER MY GRANDSON.

28:42.042 --> 28:45.478
HE SHOT AT HIM.

28:45.478 --> 28:47.981
DID HE?

28:47.981 --> 28:51.017
♪♪♪♪

28:51.017 --> 28:53.987
WELL, HE COULDN'T HAVE
KNOWN WHO HE WAS.

28:53.987 --> 28:56.189
WHATEVER
THE HELL HE DID,

28:56.189 --> 28:59.125
HE JUST
LIVED UP TO HIS NAME.

28:59.125 --> 29:00.934
I'M GOING TO
GIVE HIM A WAR.

29:00.934 --> 29:02.636
ROSE. ROSE.

29:02.636 --> 29:04.705
HE'S A SNOT‐NOSED KID
OFF THE STREET

29:04.705 --> 29:06.206
WHO THINKS
HE'S A GANGSTER.

29:06.206 --> 29:09.209
YES, I KNOW THAT.

29:09.209 --> 29:11.311
THESE ARE DIFFERENT TIMES, ROSE.
YOU CAN'T DO THIS.

29:11.311 --> 29:13.279
YOU GO DOWN THIS ROAD,
IT'S ALL ABOUT POWER.

29:13.279 --> 29:16.216
IT'S GOING TO ‐‐
HE GAVE ME NO CHOICE.

29:18.585 --> 29:20.654
LISTEN TO ME, OKAY?

29:20.654 --> 29:22.388
