IT'S GOING TO GET

29:22.388 --> 29:26.727
VERY, VERY HEATED
AROUND HERE.

29:26.727 --> 29:29.596
WHY WOULD YOU WORRY
ABOUT HEAT?

29:35.536 --> 29:38.672
YOU REALIZE WE'RE IN THIS THING
DEEP TOGETHER, RIGHT?

29:38.672 --> 29:41.875
YEAH, WE ARE.

29:41.875 --> 29:43.443
SO, IF YOU GO DOWN,

29:43.443 --> 29:45.812
