TO BE CONCERNED ABOUT.

29:45.812 --> 29:48.949
SO, ARE YOU TRYING TO TELL ME
I SHOULD JUST LET THIS GO?

29:48.949 --> 29:50.751
NO.
LISTEN TO ME.

29:50.751 --> 29:54.387
I'M NOT TRYING TO TELL YOU
YOU SHOULD LET IT GO AT ALL!

29:54.387 --> 29:55.956
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?!
I'M TRYING TO TELL YOU

29:55.956 --> 29:57.290
YOU SHOULD LET ME
TALK TO HIM.

29:57.290 --> 29:58.391
TALK TO HIM?!
YES!

29:58.391 --> 30:00.634
TALK?
YES.

30:00.634 --> 30:02.435
I'LL TALK TO HIM.

30:02.435 --> 30:04.137
YOU STAY OUT OF IT.

30:04.137 --> 30:07.941
WHY THE HELL WOULD YOU
WANT TO PROTECT HIM?

30:07.941 --> 30:09.375
I'M NOT TRYING
TO PROTECT HIM.

30:09.375 --> 30:11.812
I WANT TO TALK TO HIM
AND LET HIM KNOW WHAT HE DID

30:11.812 --> 30:13.113
AND WHO HE DID IT TO.

30:13.113 --> 30:17.618
I DON'T GIVE A RAT'S ASS
ABOUT THIS KID.

30:17.618 --> 30:20.320
ROSE, YOU'RE
A SMART WOMAN.

30:20.320 --> 30:23.423
YOU KNOW THAT THIS THING
WILL GET MESSY.

30:23.423 --> 30:25.759
WITH EVERYTHING THAT'S BEEN
GOING DOWN WITH MY SON

30:25.759 --> 30:27.961
AND THAT CASTILLE KID,

30:27.961 --> 30:30.931
IF YOU TAKE THIS ROUTE,
IT COULD DESTROY ME.

30:30.931 --> 30:34.467
I DON'T GIVE A DAMN
ABOUT YOU OR THAT KID.

30:34.467 --> 30:36.102
I KNOW THAT.

30:36.102 --> 30:38.071
HELL, I DIDN'T KNOW
YOU CAME HERE

30:38.071 --> 30:39.339
TO GIVE ME
YOUR PERMISSION

30:39.339 --> 30:40.974
OR TRY TO TALK ME
OUT OF SOMETHING

30:40.974 --> 30:42.075
THAT'S ALREADY
BEEN DECIDED.

30:42.075 --> 30:45.378
I UNDERSTAND THAT, ROSE,
AND I'M SORRY,

30:45.378 --> 30:48.481
BUT YOU NEED TO
UNDERSTAND THINGS, TOO.

30:48.481 --> 30:52.385
♪♪♪♪

30:52.385 --> 30:55.756
YOU KNOW, I SHOULD
BLAME YOU FOR THIS.

30:55.756 --> 30:58.792
OH, ROSE.
YOU GOT HIM OUT!

30:58.792 --> 31:02.869
I DIDN'T KNOW THAT
HE KNEW YOUR GRANDSON.

31:02.869 --> 31:05.471
WELL, HE DOESN'T.

31:05.471 --> 31:07.073
♪♪♪♪

31:07.073 --> 31:09.676
[ SCOFFS ]
SO HOW IS HE?

31:09.676 --> 31:11.477
IS HE GOING TO BE OKAY?

31:11.477 --> 31:13.246
HE WASN'T SHOT.

31:13.246 --> 31:16.282
♪♪♪♪

31:18.685 --> 31:20.554
ARE YOU TELLING ME
THAT YOU ARE WILLING

31:20.554 --> 31:22.055
TO GO THROUGH
ALL OF THIS TROUBLE

31:22.055 --> 31:23.757
TO CAUSE THIS...STORM,

31:23.757 --> 31:26.827
AND YOUR GRANDSON
WASN'T EVEN SHOT?

31:26.827 --> 31:29.095
ARE YOU KIDDING ME?

31:29.095 --> 31:31.497
I NEED TO SEND
A CLEAR MESSAGE

31:31.497 --> 31:34.200
THAT THE MALONES
ARE NOT TO BE...WITH EVER!

31:34.200 --> 31:38.338
I THINK THIS CHILD UNDERSTANDS
THAT, ROSE, ALREADY!

31:38.338 --> 31:42.543
WELL, ONCE IN A WHILE,
WE NEED TO REBROADCAST IT.

31:42.543 --> 31:45.679
♪♪♪♪

31:45.679 --> 31:47.047
ROSE.

31:47.047 --> 31:48.114
JIM.

31:48.114 --> 31:50.016
CALL HIM.

31:52.085 --> 31:54.087
ALL RIGHT, I WILL ‐‐
I WILL CALL HIM.

31:54.087 --> 31:55.889
NOW!

31:55.889 --> 31:58.925
♪♪♪♪

32:06.406 --> 32:08.709
[ CELLPHONE CLICKING,
BEEPS ]

32:08.709 --> 32:11.077
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

32:15.882 --> 32:18.251
YO.

32:18.251 --> 32:21.487
WAR.

32:21.487 --> 32:23.123
WHAT?

32:23.123 --> 32:25.025
THIS IS JIM.

32:25.025 --> 32:28.028
MAN,
I KNOW WHO THIS IS.

32:28.028 --> 32:32.065
WHERE ARE YOU?
WE NEED TO TALK.

32:32.065 --> 32:33.466
WHAT YOU NEED
TO TALK TO ME ABOUT, MAN?

32:33.466 --> 32:34.801
Because
we have ourselves

32:34.801 --> 32:37.203
A LITTLE SITUATION
HERE, WARRICK.

32:37.203 --> 32:39.272
LOOK, I AIN'T KNOW THAT LITTLE
KID WAS IN THERE, ALL RIGHT?

32:39.272 --> 32:41.141
WHAT? WHAT KID?

32:41.141 --> 32:42.809
CANDACE SON,
THE ONE THAT GOT SHOT.

32:42.809 --> 32:45.378
What?
YEAH.

32:45.378 --> 32:47.848
YOU SHOT A KID?

32:47.848 --> 32:51.552
LOOK, I AIN'T KNOW HE WAS
IN THERE, ALL RIGHT?

32:51.552 --> 32:52.986
WARRICK, YOU NEED
TO UNDERSTAND SOMETHING.

32:52.986 --> 32:54.921
WHERE ARE YOU?
WE NEED TO TALK.

32:54.921 --> 32:56.289
WHAT YOU NEED
TO TALK TO ME ABOUT?

32:56.289 --> 33:00.293
WARRICK, YOU SHOT
AT THE WRONG PERSON.

33:00.293 --> 33:02.102
LOOK, MAN, THAT LITTLE KID
SHOULDN'T HAVE BEEN IN THERE.

33:02.102 --> 33:03.770
I'M NOT TALKING ABOUT
THAT KID, WARRICK!

33:03.770 --> 33:06.039
I'M TALKING ABOUT
ANOTHER KID ENTIRELY!

33:06.039 --> 33:08.675
MITCH?
Mitch.

33:08.675 --> 33:10.677
MAN, I KNOW YOU AIN'T CALL ME
ABOUT THAT BITCH‐ASS.

33:10.677 --> 33:12.345
HE'S A MALONE,
WARRICK.

33:12.345 --> 33:14.915
YOU HAVE JUST PISSED OFF
THE WRONG PEOPLE IN THIS TOWN.

33:14.915 --> 33:17.618
MAN, I DON'T GIVE A DAMN!
YOU THINK I'M SCARED?

33:17.618 --> 33:19.653
WARRICK,
LET ME HELP YOU.

33:19.653 --> 33:21.421
WHY YOU WANT TO HELP ME?

33:21.421 --> 33:24.558
YOU DIDN'T GET MY PACKAGE YET,
RIGHT? THE PHOTOS?

33:24.558 --> 33:25.726
YEAH.

33:25.726 --> 33:27.127
WELL, UNTIL YOU DO,

33:27.127 --> 33:30.063
I NEED TO MAKE SURE
THAT YOU'RE SAFE.

33:30.063 --> 33:31.532
WHAT HAPPENS
AFTER I GET THEM?

33:31.532 --> 33:33.567
THEN I NEED TO MAKE SURE
YOU GET YOUR ASS

33:33.567 --> 33:36.436
OUT OF SAVANNAH SAFE.

33:36.436 --> 33:37.671
MAN, I AIN'T
LEAVING SAVANNAH.

33:37.671 --> 33:39.673
YOU HAVE TO LEAVE
SAVANNAH, WARRICK.

33:39.673 --> 33:42.643
♪♪♪♪

33:42.643 --> 33:43.944
LOOK, MAN ‐‐
Where are you?

33:43.944 --> 33:45.411
I'LL COME GET YOU.

33:45.411 --> 33:46.980
NAH, THAT AIN'T
HAPPENING.

33:46.980 --> 33:48.148
Warrick.

33:48.148 --> 33:50.116
NO, THAT
AIN'T HAPPENING.

33:50.116 --> 33:52.485
OKAY.

33:52.485 --> 33:53.854
WHEN DO YOU THINK
YOU'LL HAVE MY PHOTOS?

33:53.854 --> 33:55.756
LOOK, MAN,
I'M WORKING ON IT.

33:55.756 --> 33:57.891
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

33:57.891 --> 34:00.293
ALL RIGHT,
UNTIL THEN ‐‐

34:00.293 --> 34:03.637
WARRICK?

34:03.637 --> 34:07.508
I'M TRIED OF THIS, MAN.

34:07.508 --> 34:10.844
♪♪♪♪

34:10.844 --> 34:14.347
HE HUNG UP.

34:14.347 --> 34:16.382
GIVE ME THE NUMBER.

34:16.382 --> 34:19.786
♪♪♪♪

34:19.786 --> 34:22.122
HAVE HIM
TAKE IT OFF OF THAT.

34:22.122 --> 34:27.293
TRACE THIS.
FIND THAT SON OF A BITCH.

34:27.293 --> 34:31.297
MAMA ROSE,
PLEASE DON'T DO THIS.

34:31.297 --> 34:34.034
LET ME GO FIND HIM,
ALL RIGHT?

34:34.034 --> 34:36.069
LET'S NOT DO IT AGAIN.

34:38.271 --> 34:41.675
YOU BETTER FIND HIM
BEFORE I DO.

34:41.675 --> 34:46.146
I'LL DO MY BEST.

34:46.146 --> 34:49.516
MAMA ROSE,
I NEED YOU TO CONSIDER

34:49.516 --> 34:52.786
THE ROAD YOU'RE GOING DOWN,
OKAY? BELIEVE ME.

34:52.786 --> 34:58.391
THIS STREET THUG IS NOT
WORTH YOUR TROUBLE.

34:58.391 --> 35:01.434
GO.

35:01.434 --> 35:03.269
GO.

35:03.269 --> 35:05.639
NOW. GET OUT.

35:05.639 --> 35:08.709
♪♪♪♪

35:08.709 --> 35:11.411
I'VE BEEN WATCHING
THE NEWS.

35:11.411 --> 35:17.283
ALL I SEE ABOUT D. A. SALLISON
IS THAT SHE'S MISSING.

35:17.283 --> 35:20.353
WHAT ARE YOUR PLANS
FOR THE BODY?

35:20.353 --> 35:23.389
♪♪♪♪

35:34.500 --> 35:36.603
THANKS FOR THE DRINK.

35:36.603 --> 35:39.606
♪♪♪♪

36:03.269 --> 36:05.539
David, it's Jim.
David: YES, JIM?

36:05.539 --> 36:07.508
I just left Mama Rose.

36:07.508 --> 36:09.843
WHAT? WHY?

36:09.843 --> 36:12.178
She's really pissed
about this War kid.

36:12.178 --> 36:14.014
WHAT THE HELL DID HE DO?

36:14.014 --> 36:16.617
HE TOOK A SHOT
AT HER GRANDSON.

36:16.617 --> 36:19.119
OH, DAMN IT.

36:19.119 --> 36:20.787
JIM, YOU KNOW
THIS IS A POWDER KEG.

36:20.787 --> 36:23.123
YEAH. YEAH,
I KNOW THAT, DAVE.

36:23.123 --> 36:25.125
AND WE CANNOT AFFORD
TO HAVE RULES UPSET,

36:25.125 --> 36:26.459
ESPECIALLY NOW.

36:26.459 --> 36:27.460
YOU'RE NOT ACTUALLY
TELLING ME ANYTHING

36:27.460 --> 36:29.796
I DON'T ALREADY KNOW,
DAVID.

36:29.796 --> 36:31.865
You have a plan?

36:31.865 --> 36:33.433
THIS GUY
THAT FOUND WYATT.

36:33.433 --> 36:35.602
OSCAR.
YEAH. YEAH, OSCAR.

36:35.602 --> 36:38.739
WHAT ABOUT HIM?
CAN HE BE TRUSTED?

36:38.739 --> 36:41.341
YES, I THINK SO.
You think so?

36:41.341 --> 36:42.509
DAVID, I DON'T NEED
YOU TO THINK SO.

36:42.509 --> 36:45.178
I NEED YOU TO BE DAMN SURE.
CAN HE BE TRUSTED?

36:45.178 --> 36:48.348
YES, JIM,
I'VE USED HIM FOR YEARS.

36:48.348 --> 36:50.183
WHAT DO YOU HAVE
ON HIM?

36:50.183 --> 36:52.285
GOT HIM PROBATION.
SO, IF HE SCREWS UP,

36:52.285 --> 36:53.987
WE CAN SEND HIS ASS
RIGHT BACK TO JAIL, RIGHT?

36:53.987 --> 36:57.724
WELL, HIS PROBATION
IS UP NOW.

36:57.724 --> 36:59.726
WE NEED LEVERAGE,
DAVID.

36:59.726 --> 37:01.300
FINE, FINE. I ‐‐

37:01.300 --> 37:03.469
MAYBE I CAN COME UP
WITH SOMETHING.

37:03.469 --> 37:05.972
ALL RIGHT,
YOU DO THAT.

37:05.972 --> 37:09.876
SO, WHAT'S THE PLAN?

37:09.876 --> 37:11.477
ROSE GOT HIS NUMBER
OFF MY PHONE.

37:11.477 --> 37:13.379
WE HAVE TO FIND HIM
BEFORE SHE DOES.

37:13.379 --> 37:15.381
OKAY, HE CAN TRACK THAT.

37:15.381 --> 37:16.783
SHE HAS THAT
PACKAGE OF OURS.

37:16.783 --> 37:18.918
WE NEED TO MAKE DAMN SURE
THAT SHE GETS RID OF IT.

37:18.918 --> 37:21.121
YES, I KNOW.

37:21.121 --> 37:24.390
OSCAR HAS TO FIND HIM, DAVID.
HE'S GOT TO FIND WAR.

37:24.390 --> 37:26.760
OKAY, I'M ON IT.

37:26.760 --> 37:29.930
OKAY, GOOD.
HEY, WHERE ARE YOU?

37:29.930 --> 37:31.665
I'M ON MY WAY
TO ST. CLOUD HOSPITAL

37:31.665 --> 37:33.466
TO TALK TO JEFFERY.

37:33.466 --> 37:36.703
I'll meet you there.
MM.

37:36.703 --> 37:38.471
[ BEEP ]

37:38.471 --> 37:41.508
♪♪♪♪

37:53.253 --> 37:54.320
MS. YOUNG?

37:54.320 --> 37:55.455
LOOK, RIGHT NOW
IS NOT THE TIME TO TALK.

37:55.455 --> 37:57.390
IT'LL ONLY TAKE
A SECOND.

37:57.390 --> 37:59.926
I'M DETECTIVE LOGAN.

37:59.926 --> 38:01.968
I'M SORRY
ABOUT YOUR GRANDSON.

38:01.968 --> 38:03.637
WHAT IS THIS?

38:03.637 --> 38:05.706
WE JUST NEED HER
TO ANSWER SOME QUESTIONS

38:05.706 --> 38:07.040
ABOUT THIS SHOOTING.

38:07.040 --> 38:08.308
NOT NOW.
THIS ISN'T A GOOD TIME.

38:08.308 --> 38:11.444
NO, IT'S ‐‐ IT'S BETTER
THE FRESHER IT IS IN HER MEMORY.

38:11.444 --> 38:12.913
WELL, YOU CAN
CALL HER TOMORROW.

38:12.913 --> 38:15.181
I JUST HAVE
ONE QUESTION.

38:15.181 --> 38:20.921
HIS NAME IS
WARRICK MENCY LEWIS.

38:20.921 --> 38:24.858
AND HE BUSTED INTO OUR ROOM
AND GOT INTO A FIGHT

38:24.858 --> 38:27.360
WITH MY SON
AND THIS BOY HERE, MITCHELL,

38:27.360 --> 38:29.996
LOOKING
FOR MY DAUGHTER.

38:29.996 --> 38:31.665
HER DAUGHTER IS
CANDACE YOUNG.

38:31.665 --> 38:34.167
YEAH, SO,
SHE WASN'T THERE?

38:34.167 --> 38:35.268
MNH‐MNH.

38:35.268 --> 38:36.302
WHY WAS
HE LOOKING FOR HER?

38:36.302 --> 38:37.638
BECAUSE
THEY'RE BOTH EVIL.

38:37.638 --> 38:38.905
OKAY, WE'RE
DONE TALKING.

38:38.905 --> 38:40.240
OH, JUST ONE MORE,
PLEASE.

38:40.240 --> 38:42.876
LOOK,
SHE DONE TALKING.

38:42.876 --> 38:45.662
WELL, WILL YOU TALK TO US?
YOU'RE BENNY.

38:48.882 --> 38:52.485
HOW DO YOU KNOW THAT.
CANDACE'S BROTHER?

38:52.485 --> 38:54.788
YEAH.
OKAY, CAN YOU?

38:54.788 --> 38:59.425
♪♪♪♪

38:59.425 --> 39:02.202
SURE.

39:02.202 --> 39:04.270
AND YOU WERE THERE
WHEN ALL THIS HAPPENED?

39:04.270 --> 39:05.972
YEAH.
WHAT'S YOUR NAME?

39:05.972 --> 39:08.441
MITCH.
MITCH MALONE.

39:10.410 --> 39:12.679
MALONE?
UH‐HUH.

39:12.679 --> 39:14.748
AS IN GARY
AND FREDRICO MALONE?

39:14.748 --> 39:16.717
YEAH.

39:16.717 --> 39:18.284
SON?

39:18.284 --> 39:19.586
GRANDSON.

39:19.586 --> 39:22.255
OKAY, SO, IF YOU TWO DON'T MIND,
WILL YOU TALK TO US?

39:22.255 --> 39:24.858
SHE ALREADY SAID EVERYTHING
WE WOULD KNOW ANYWAY.

39:24.858 --> 39:26.627
PLEASE MAKE THIS EASY
AND INDULGE US.

39:26.627 --> 39:28.428
THERE IT IS.
IT'S EASY. GO.

39:30.831 --> 39:34.000
WANT TO TELL US
WHAT HAPPENED?

39:34.000 --> 39:35.368
SHE ALREADY TOLD YOU.

39:35.368 --> 39:37.538
YEAH, BUT WHY
WERE YOU THERE?

39:37.538 --> 39:40.240
WELL, YOU SEE, IT'S A MOTEL,
SO WE RENTED A ROOM THERE.

39:40.240 --> 39:42.509
THAT'S WHY.

39:42.509 --> 39:44.210
AND YOU?

39:44.210 --> 39:47.213
WE'RE FRIENDS.

39:47.213 --> 39:49.382
WAS THIS A DRUG THING?
NOW, COME ON, MAN.

39:49.382 --> 39:50.851
I NEED TO KNOW.

39:50.851 --> 39:52.753
JUST TAKE IT EASY, ALL RIGHT?
HIS NEPHEW JUST GOT KILLED.

39:52.753 --> 39:55.055
WHAT ABOUT
THIS WAR PERSON?

39:55.055 --> 39:58.024
♪♪♪♪

39:58.024 --> 40:00.293
YEAH, MAN.
CHECK HIS RECORD.

40:00.293 --> 40:02.903
YEAH, WE WILL.
YOU SHOULD.

40:02.903 --> 40:06.807
SO, CANDACE YOUNG.
SHE'S YOUR SISTER?

40:06.807 --> 40:10.110
THAT'S RIGHT.
AND SHE WASN'T THERE?

40:10.110 --> 40:13.379
NOPE.
WHERE IS SHE?

40:13.379 --> 40:14.681
I DON'T KNOW.

40:14.681 --> 40:16.382
I CALLED HER.
SHE WON'T RETURN MY CALLS.

40:16.382 --> 40:18.519
HEY, DO YOU HAVE A NUMBER THAT
YOU CAN GIVE TO US?

40:18.519 --> 40:19.953
NOPE.

40:19.953 --> 40:21.855
BUT YOU JUST SAID
THAT YOU TRIED TO CALL?

40:21.855 --> 40:26.993
LOOK, I'M NOT GIVING YOU
MY SISTER'S NUMBER, ALL RIGHT?

40:26.993 --> 40:29.329
YOU KNOW SHE'S WANTED,
RIGHT?

40:29.329 --> 40:31.532
YEAH, I HEARD.

40:31.532 --> 40:34.100
SO, THEN YOU SHOULD
TRY TO HELP HER.

40:34.100 --> 40:35.669
ALL RIGHT, WELL,
YOU AIN'T GETTING HELP FROM ME,

40:35.669 --> 40:39.339
SO LOOK SOMEWHERE ELSE.

40:39.339 --> 40:41.441
HOW TALL ARE YOU?

40:41.441 --> 40:42.843
WHY?

40:42.843 --> 40:45.646
WHAT, ABOUT 6'1"?
I'M TALLER THAN YOU. WHY?

40:45.646 --> 40:47.213
WELL, BECAUSE WE KNOW
THAT TWO PEOPLE

40:47.213 --> 40:48.882
STABBED QUINCY MAXWELL,

40:48.882 --> 40:50.350
AND ONE OF THEM JUST HAPPENS
TO BE YOUR HEIGHT.

40:50.350 --> 40:53.119
LISTEN, YOU BETTER GET OUT OF
HERE WITH ALL THAT, ALL RIGHT?

40:53.119 --> 40:54.354
I JUST LOST MY NEPHEW.
HE'S DEAD.

40:54.354 --> 40:55.989
AND NOW YOU TALKING
TO BE ABOUT THIS BULL...?

40:55.989 --> 40:58.058
GET OUT OF HERE.
DO YOU WEAR BRACELETS?

40:58.058 --> 40:59.826
YOU GOT EYES.
OBVIOUSLY NOT.

40:59.826 --> 41:01.201
LOOK, YOU CAN TALK
TO ME HERE AND NOW,

41:01.201 --> 41:02.769
OR YOU CAN TALK TO ME
DOWN AT THE STATION.

41:02.769 --> 41:04.070
YOU CAN'T
GET ME DOWN THERE

41:04.070 --> 41:06.740
WITHOUT ARRESTING ME ANYWAYS,
SO IT DON'T MATTER.

41:06.740 --> 41:09.275
OKAY.
OKAY, WHAT?

41:09.275 --> 41:11.111
BENJAMIN YOUNG...
THAT'S MY NAME.

41:11.111 --> 41:13.113
...YOU'RE UNDER ARREST FOR
THE MURDER OF QUINCY MAXWELL.

41:13.113 --> 41:14.748
OH, MY GOD.
MAN, TAKE HIM IN.

41:14.748 --> 41:15.916
WHAT THE HELL ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

41:15.916 --> 41:17.684
THAT'S A JOKE.
BEHIND YOUR BACK.

41:17.684 --> 41:19.786
EASY FOR YOU TO SAY.

41:19.786 --> 41:22.823
♪♪♪♪

41:24.791 --> 41:26.426
IS THAT COP
STILL OUT THERE?

41:26.426 --> 41:28.929
<i>NEXT ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

41:28.929 --> 41:30.631
THIS GUYS IS NUTS.

41:30.631 --> 41:32.198
YOU MAY WANT
TO GO SEE YOUR SON.

41:32.198 --> 41:34.000
YOU TELL ME WHAT THE HELL
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT RIGHT NOW.

41:34.000 --> 41:35.869
WHY THE HELL IS HE HERE
IN THE HOSPITAL?

41:35.869 --> 41:36.870
YOU REALLY SHOULDN'T
BE GETTING ‐‐

41:36.870 --> 41:39.305
NO, YOU CAN JUST GO!
I'M TRYING TO HELP.

41:39.305 --> 41:41.241
LEAVE!
JUST LEAVE!

41:41.241 --> 41:43.109
I DON'T ‐‐

41:43.109 --> 41:44.511
IT'S FINE.
THERE'S NO CAMERAS IN HERE.

41:44.511 --> 41:45.812
I ALREADY CHECKED.

41:47.380 --> 41:49.850
I'M GLAD I LEFT YOU.
ARE YOU SURE YOU'RE GONE?

41:49.850 --> 41:51.785
YOU DON'T WANT TO MESS
WITH THESE PEOPLE.

41:51.785 --> 41:53.587
IF THEY SMELL YOU COMING
OR THEY FEEL THREATENED BY YOU,

41:53.587 --> 41:55.355
THEY WILL COME FOR YOU.

41:55.355 --> 41:57.390
I TOLD YOU
I'LL DO IT.
